</div>
</div>
    
    <div class="wpd-comment-text">
    <p>jgh, the trick to minimal streakiness is to fold the berries in, not mix them. So lift the batter up and over the berries, don&#8217;t stir them around.</p>
<p>Emily, whoops! My mistake. Kimmy was chopping the lavender, I guess that&#8217;s why I got mixed up.</p>

</div>
