    <div class="wpd-comment-text">
    <p>The VWAV recipe is 2 Tbl, I assumed we used that amount.  These scones are amazing!  I adore lavender and the flavor really came through.  Fine, Emily, you can have credit for the scones, but without my lavender they wouldn&#8217;t have been as awesome. 😉</p>

</div>
