    <div class="wpd-comment-text">
    <p>These look great!  The elderberries in my yard are finally getting ripe and I think they will work well in this recipe.  Are you using a commercial almond milk or homemade?  I know the commercial ones usually have sweeteners and other ingredients (including more almond flavor).</p>

</div>
