</div>
    
    <div class="wpd-comment-text">
    <p>So great! I added blue poppy seeds. Next time maybe I&#8217;ll try some lemon something too? My batch actually made 18. and I used maple to cut out the sugar. And cuz I&#8217;m a freak i added up the calories and its like 146 per if anyone was wondering I used blueberries. Which is like super awesome. I don&#8217;t comment on anything ever&#8230; but this was really fun to make! Thanks so much!</p>

