        <a class='wc_tw' rel='noreferrer' target='_blank' href='https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=[&#8230;] I won’t duplicate the recipe here f... &url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theppk.com%2F2008%2F08%2Fberry-week-day-1-marionberry-lavender-scones%2F%23comment-24626' title='Share On X'><i class='wpf-cta' aria-hidden='true'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 512 512'><path d='M389.2 48h70.6L305.6 224.2 487 464H345L233.7 318.6 106.5 464H35.8L200.7 275.5 26.8 48H172.4L272.9 180.9 389.2 48zM364.4 421.8h39.1L151.1 88h-42L364.4 421.8z'/></svg></i></a>
