    <div class="wpd-comment-text">
    <p>I made these w/blackberries and rosemary. Delicious!  I love your stuff. This week&#8217;s menu is all Vegan w/a Vengence.  I&#8217;m looking for a good curry leaf scone recipe&#8230;anyone have ideas in mind: I&#8217;m thinking golden raisens, walnuts, masala mixture and curry leaf.  Any other ideas, e-mail me, <a href="mailto:ileyanicole@gmail.com">ileyanicole@gmail.com</a></p>

