    <div class="wpd-comment-text">
    <p>I just made these, and they smell delicious. I mostly followed the recipe (but using dried lavender) and subbing 2 cups spelt flour as I was almost out of whole wheat pasty. This must have been a huge mistake because my scones flattened out from the nice scoop shape that they previously were. Unless over mixing would have been the culprit?</p>

</div>
