</div>
</div>
    
    <div class="wpd-comment-text">
    <p>I just made these and they are lovely. I substituted dried lavender for the fresh but they are a little heavy on the lavender. I used about 1.5 T. i think I would go for like 1 or a little less than 1 next time. Besides that they were awesome except for the fact that I dropped a tray on the floor 🙁<br />
I like the idea of lemon and poppyseed. Would be a nice addition.</p>

</div>
