    <div class="wpd-comment-text">
    <p>I was reading though the comments and it was kind of unclear about whether the baking powder was a typo or not. I just put these in the oven with the 2 tablespoons of BP and THEN read the comments&#8230;now I am wondering about the BP. I did kind of wonder when I added it, like &#8220;whoa, 2 tablespoons is a ton, but hey, I&#8217;ve never made scones before and Isa has never let me down&#8230;&#8221; </p>
<p>So&#8230;was it a typo or not? 🙂</p>

</div>
